<h4 id="_383-赎金信" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_383-赎金信" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/ransom-note/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">383. 赎金信<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h4>
